            . I am an officer. On the 8th of September, about a quarter past seven o'clock, I was in <placeName id="t18270913-145-crimeloc833">Broad-street, St. Giles</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18270913-145-crimeloc833" type="placeName" value="Broad-street, St. Giles"></interp>
