                  </persName>
            . I live in St. Giles; these trousers hung inside my door; they were pinned to a coat; it would require a strong pull to get them down.</p>
               <p>SIMPSON's Defence. I saw a waistcoat piece in the window; I was looking at it; the other prisoner came and asked the time, I felt some one brush by me - I looked at the window again, and a man came up, and said, "I have got you;" he would not tell me what for.</p>
